[Student "S"]
{Following your Jacoby 2NT response, partner bids 3\H, showing a singleton. What is your next bid? 

Your \H holding hasn't been enhanced by partner's singleton. You feel like just signing off at 4\S but since you can show the \D control below that level you bid 4\D. It didn't matter since partner now signs off at 4\S.}

